Populate mid/, nono/, and pprof/ from the OpenBSD working tree:

  ksh /usr/ports/openbsd-wip/devel/grok-build/populate-remaining.sh

or:

  cp -R /home/grokbuild/git/sw/grok-build/vendor/{mid,nono,pprof} \
    /usr/ports/openbsd-wip/devel/grok-build/files/vendor/

Fallback vendor trees: /tlaptop.a/grokbuild/vendor/
